間腦症候群的特徵是一種天生罕見擁有發育停滯[[神經系統|神經系統]]的[[疾病|疾病]]。儘管生理正常或略有減少熱量攝入、運動機能亢進、和亢奮感，皆有嚴重消瘦的現象。皮膚蒼白不太常見，無[[貧血|貧血]]、[[低血糖|低血糖]]和[[低血壓|低血壓]]<ref group="醫學" name="pmid25729396">{{cite journal| author = Kim A, Moon JS, Yang HR, Chang JY, Ko JS, Seo JK| title = Diencephalic syndrome: a frequently neglected cause of failure to thrive in infants| journal = Korean J Pediatr| volume = 58| issue = 1| pages = 28-32|date= Jan 2015| pmid = 25729396}}</ref>。間腦症候群可能會影響到自身的成長，也可能導致致命的原因，未能成長茁壯的幼兒平均只有七個月的年齡<ref group="醫學" name="pmid25729396"/>。值得注意的是該症狀不與發育遲緩有關，而是與腦積水有關<ref group="醫學" name="pmid15930202">{{cite journal| author = Fleischman A1, Brue C, Poussaint TY, Kieran M, Pomeroy SL, Goumnerova L, Scott RM, Cohen LE| title = Diencephalic syndrome: a cause of failure to thrive and a model of partial growth hormone resistance| journal = Pediatrics| volume = 115| issue = 6| pages = 724–6|date= June 2005| pmid = 15930202}}</ref>。

間腦症候群於1951年由[[罗素|罗素]]首次介紹<ref>{{cite journal| author = Russell A| title = A diencephalic syndrome of emaciation in infancy and childhood| url = https://archive.org/details/sim_archives-of-disease-in-childhood_1951-06_26_127/page/274| journal = Arch Dis Child| volume = 26| issue = | pages = 274|date = 1951}}</ref>。雖然因為有過多的β促脂解素的分泌<ref group="醫學" name="pmid25729396"/>和[[代謝|代謝]]需求整體上升<ref group="醫學" name="pmid8501572">{{cite journal| author = Vlachopapadopoulou E, Tracey KJ, Capella M, Gilker C, Matthews DE| title = Increased energy expenditure in a patient with diencephalic syndrome| journal = J Pediatr| volume = 112| issue = 6| pages = 922-4|date= June 1993| pmid = 8501572}}</ref>，使不適當高的[[生長激素|生長激素]]釋放已被提出<ref  group="醫學" name="pmid7438472">{{cite journal| author = Drop SL, Guyda HJ, Colle E| title = Inappropriate growth hormone release in the diencephalic syndrome of childhood: case report and 4 year endocrinological follow-up| url = https://archive.org/details/sim_clinical-endocrinology_1980-08_13_2/page/181| journal = Clin Endocrinol (Oxf)| volume = 13| issue = 2| pages = 181-7|date = August 1980| pmid = 7438472}}</ref>，但是位於下丘腦 - 光視交叉區，通常會引起如低級別膠質瘤或星形細胞瘤的[[腦腫瘤|腦腫瘤]]，然而尚未了解到如何影響到食慾和新陳代謝所引起的間腦症候群。

